                    <p class="section-title bg-white text-start text-primary pe-3">About Us</p>
                    <h1 class="mb-4">Learn More About Our Internet-Based Junkshop</h1>
                    <p class="mb-4">Our scrap collection platform is motivated by a personal goal to change the way junkshops and users engage with their scraps. We have a strong dedication to sustainability and community, and we are enthusiastic about transforming the scrap management and recycling field. Our mission is driven by the aspiration to make a positive impact on the environment and provide convenient and easily accessible options for scrap disposal, guaranteeing a better future for future generations.</p>
                    <div class="row g-5 pt-2 mb-5">
                        <div class="col-sm-6">
                            <img class="img-fluid mb-4" src="img/services-pickup.png" alt="" width="30%">                            <h5 class="mb-3">Dedicated Services</h5>
                            <span>It offers convenient disposal and recycling services, allowing customers to schedule pickups for a wide range of scraps. With eco-friendly disposal methods and transparent pricing, they provide a hassle-free solution for decluttering while minimizing environmental impact.</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-6">
                            <img class="img-fluid mb-4" src="img/scraps-waste.png" alt="" width="30%">
                            <h5 class="mb-3">Scrap Materials</h5>
                            <span>These services handle various scrap materials, including steel, plastics, karton, paper, yero, and copper, ensuring proper recycling and disposal to promote sustainability. By recycling items, they contribute to reducing waste and conserving resources.</span>
                        </div>
