                        <div>
                            <h2 class="text-white mb-3">Vision</h2>
                            <p class="text-white mb-4">We envision becoming the leading platform in the recycling industry and to foster a culture of sustainability through seamless transactions and collaboration among communities, Barangays, small junkshops, and large recycling centers. Also, create a circular economy where used products are turned into new ones and maximizing recycling.</p>
                        </div>
