                        <div>
                            <h2 class="text-white mb-3">Mission</h2>
                            <p class="text-white mb-4">We aim for a waste-free world by connecting scrap collectors, local junkshops, and large recycling centers through an integrated digital platform. We aim to revolutionize waste management practices and drive economic growth by making recycling accessible and profitable for everyone involved.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay="0.7s">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-start">
                        <img class="img-fluid rounded" src="img/goal.jpg" alt="" style="width: 100px; height: 100px; object-fit: cover; margin-right: 20px;">
                        <div>
                            <h2 class="text-white mb-3">Goal</h2>
                            <p class="text-white mb-4">Our objective is to simplify and make recycling available to all, including institutions, by consistently innovating with technology. This involves using a digital platform for conducting transactions, maintaining logs, recording history, and analyzing data. We are committed to ensuring that all collected scraps are recycled in the proper manner. Furthermore, we are dedicated to expanding our network and boosting the amount of scrap materials processed each year.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
